DARE
Hot night,
steamy night,
white sheet,
love is sweet,
touching you,
adoring you,
feel your lips.
the last breathe,
caress your body,
feel you essence,
stay silence,
feel malice,
feel so soft,
never leave,
never since,
look at me,
I can see,
touching you,
touching me,
feel undone,
passion will come,
sweat bodies,
warm room,
last passion,
sexy doom,
take me above,
where is the love?
show me how,
things can change,
passion it was,
love is here,
we are no more,
two stranger,
in this night dare.

